      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-level2",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is operated under a documented software quality assurance plan including version control, regression test suite (>200 canonical cases), and traceable build environment. SQA documentation meets ASME V&V 40 Gradation 2 requirements; independent code review elevates achieved level to 3.",
