      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/code-verification-level2",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests performed on manufactured solutions for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the scalar transport equation used for hemolysis index. Observed convergence rates match theoretical rates (2nd-order) within 2%. Published benchmark results (FDA nozzle, lid-driven cavity) reproduced within < 1% of reference solutions.",
