      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/discretization-error-level2",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted following Celik et al. (2008). Grid convergence index (GCI) for the normalised index of hemolysis is 3.2% on the fine mesh (14.2 million cells). Time-step sensitivity confirmed: halving time step changes NIH by < 1%. Achieved level 3 reflects full GCI reporting with uncertainty bounds propagated to QoI.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/gci-mesh-refinement-report"
    },
    {
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
