      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/solver-error-level2",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms (< 1e-6 for all equations) and global mass/momentum imbalance (< 0.01%). Floating-point round-off assessed via double-precision arithmetic and confirmed negligible relative to discretization error. Solver error budget documented and shown to be < 0.5% of NIH prediction.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/solver-convergence-report"
    },
    {
