      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/model-inputs-level2",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters (fluid density, viscosity, pump geometry dimensions, inlet velocity profiles, rotational speed) are traceable to calibrated measurements or published material data with documented uncertainty. Monte Carlo propagation of input uncertainties (1000 samples) performed; contribution of each input to NIH output variance quantified via Sobol indices. Dominant inputs (inlet flow rate, hemolysis model exponents) identified and constrained.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/model-inputs-uq-sobol-report"
    },
