      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/test-samples-level2",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis measurements obtained from three independent laboratories using the same FDA pump geometry and ASTM F1841 protocol. Sample sizes (n ≥ 6 per operating point per laboratory) provide sufficient statistical power to estimate mean NIH with < 10% coefficient of variation. Inter-laboratory variability assessed and within acceptable bounds.",
      "evidence": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/multi-lab-hemolysis-dataset-report"
